Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,梦本应是有终点的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是多么幸福的梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还是多么恐怖的梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,都会在温暖的被窝中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在妈妈的呼唤声中结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,日复一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我都会迎来不变的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不知从何时开始　梦失去了终点…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快别再哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是说话啊　亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕～　我不是亚由亚由啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　原来你会说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么盯着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非　我长得与你自幼离别的哥哥一模一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我该回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肚子饿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是肚子饿了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好　我给你买点吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么想吃的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你就没有什么喜欢吃的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:02:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,鲷鱼烧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是鲷鱼烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好　你在这里等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,假日的奇想曲\N～caprice～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了　你没有走掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过要我在这里等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真乖真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给你　我们一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真热乎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,鲷鱼烧要刚出炉的时候才最好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太好吃了　你也尝尝看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是咸的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是刚才眼泪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是　真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.06,DefaultS,,0,0,0,,所以我那时也很紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才为什么要哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不愿意说的话我今天就不再问了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我该回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再见　亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是亚由亚由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那么　我该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我会走不了的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,鲷鱼烧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:04:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想再吃鲷鱼烧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么喜欢它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还想再与我一起吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么　明天同一个时间\N\N我会在车站前的木椅那里等着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会撒谎吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拉钩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,用不着拉钩　我也一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕…　拉钩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那么　明天再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,0！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～　吓死我了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！？　这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是跑来报复我　结果又失败了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,才…　才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？　那块蒟蒻难道是你的夜宵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这…　这个…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是…　是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那就吃给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？　现…　现在就要吃吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是本来就打算要吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没有味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？　吃得爽快一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子已经饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,浪费食物是要遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真…　真琴正在吃蒟蒻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,据说是她的夜宵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蒟蒻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿成这样了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你做点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可是肚子已经不饿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你　真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的　别妨碍我的睡眠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天必须把这些整理好才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,早安　真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你清晨的问候语难道是「啊呜」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,胃一直在疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你大半夜的还贪吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没贪吃呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是为了往祐一的脸上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脸上怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走着瞧吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出门一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,您要去购物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　另外名雪忘记带便当了　所以我打算给她送去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子今天也参加田径队的练习去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让我替您去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,田径队的队长吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她训练时会是一幅什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你帮我送过来了吗　谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的建筑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这所学校是很重视社团活动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你很卖力气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为很快就是大赛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在这里观摩一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　站在角落里的话是没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？　香里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,相泽君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来参加社团活动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪和你在假日里也这么认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是名雪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想呆在家里罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,与父母吵架了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,相泽君　你已经习惯这所学校了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只上过几天课　但已经习惯一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,同班里能有认识的人在　你也方便了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说名雪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可不能给名雪添太多麻烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了她　你才能融入到班里　所以要感谢她才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,名雪虽然看上去是个乐天派　但有时却会很勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你要多多体谅她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她每次参加社团活动都会一直练习到气喘吁吁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原来这就是她爱睡觉的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想那大概是天生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…　秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起　假日里还要这么麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不　小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再说　也不能秋子阿姨自己搬这么重的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,能有祐一在　真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一君～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是祐一君啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又见面了呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕～　又撞到鼻子了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这次肯定不是我的错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她是祐一的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是个素不相识的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕～　太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非祐一讨厌我不成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今天又吃霸王餐了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是刚才卖鲷鱼烧的大叔送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你都给他添那么多麻烦了　还真是个和蔼的大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好活泼的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是水濑秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是我借住那一家的家主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,「家主」是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一家中最有权威的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,又学到了一点新知识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一　能为我介绍一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是月宫亚由　我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,月宫亚由…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是我太多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一君　你接下来打算做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正要回家去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天还必须整理一下搬家的行李才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那么　我也去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你有时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　你昨天也帮助我寻找失物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今天必须报答你才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你装模作样的干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为你会像平常那样一头栽进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我很少会做那种事情…啦…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕～　好疼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴　快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她是泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,与我一样　是借住在这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样啊　像幽灵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,下来打个招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是月宫亚由　请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我…　我是泽渡真琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你也顺便帮我整理一下行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！？　真琴也要做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是借住的人　帮点忙也是应该的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴　你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是一点力气也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呜～　用不着你来担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　这里就是祐一君的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,累死我了～　已经站不起来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你才只搬了一个箱子而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的箱子交给我　你们帮我把里边的东西拿出来摆好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃吗？　这是鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,多少有些凉了　只要你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢吃甜食吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哎　别吃得发福了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她说累了　过一会再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,三个人齐心协力　很快就做好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你和真琴都只是让行李越来越乱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呜咕～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是　我们多少帮上了一点忙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　有你们在我也轻松了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要是说过要帮忙却又没帮上忙的话　我就变成撒谎的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,亚由　你找到丢失的东西了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不　还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,丢失的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　虽然我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但她说自己正在寻找宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天祐一帮助过我一起寻找　所以今天我也想答谢他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗　希望你能早日找到它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人能走回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想向真琴道别一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大概她在午睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有空闲的时候　就随时来这里做客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,吃不吃蛋糕啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哦　你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呐　祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要为我按摩吗？　多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等我洗完澡再来给我按摩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是来给你按摩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来拿借给你的笔记的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的笔记…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是借给你了吗？　因为你说这里授课进度比以前的学校快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它忘在学校里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～？　不行啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须写作业才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明天去了学校后我会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别说晚安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,万安！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也别说万安啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想让我怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚早点睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,到了明天就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一要是没办法写作业的话也会为难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个已经超越了这些凡事的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没有超越呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那位老师是很严厉的　不认真写作业会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说　你想让我到学校去把笔记给你拿回来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧　我到学校去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,学校大概不会开门的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,或许可以找到可以打开的窗户吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,找不到的话就敲碎玻璃闯进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,外边很冷的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系　就当作是活动一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,香里叮嘱过我　不可以给你添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…　害得你连续去学校两次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我自作自受　别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好多的星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了　快点回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,…我是征讨妖魔的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比如可以说「你要退学了！」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想玩这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,征讨妖魔的使者征讨妖魔的使者征讨妖魔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子阿姨的烹饪手艺真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有机会的话尝尝她的特制果酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你想吃什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,祐一真的像是哥哥一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为要没命了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你来干什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧
